api_list.name: Latest News
api_list.description: Returns latest news from BBC live feed.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://russian-ukraine-news-feed.p.rapidapi.com/news-latest"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "russian-ukraine-news-feed.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
